<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF826A3DF8219C2F19BFB095" pageId="121" pageNumber="879" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF826A3DF8219C2F19BFB095" blockId="121.[2012,2608,2485,2904]" lastBlockId="121.[1399,2607,2919,3456]" pageId="121" pageNumber="879">
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF826A3DF8219C2F160CB1A1" box="[2013,2060,2678,2707]" country="South Sudan" name="Lakes" pageId="121" pageNumber="879">See</collectingRegion>
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF826A3DF7E29C2F16ADB1A1" baseAuthorityName="Peters" baseAuthorityYear="1870" box="[2078,2221,2678,2707]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="121" pageNumber="879" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="egregius">L. egregius</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF826A3DF7389C2F1793B1A1" authorityName="G. S. Miller" authorityYear="1931" box="[2244,2451,2678,2707]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="121" pageNumber="879" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="minor">Lasiurus minor</taxonomicName>
was previously considered a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF826A3DF6509CC7142EB189" baseAuthorityName="Muller" baseAuthorityYear="1776" box="[2476,2606,2718,2747]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="121" pageNumber="879" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="borealis">L. borealis</taxonomicName>
based on morphology. Later, it was considered a distinct species based on elec trophoretic data. Nevertheless, status of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF826A3DF8229D661654B06A" authorityName="G. S. Miller" authorityYear="1931" box="[2014,2132,2879,2904]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="121" pageNumber="879" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="minor">L. minor</taxonomicName>
1s still uncertain, and additional studies could show it as conspecific with 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF826A3DF8579D3E164BB0B2" baseAuthorityName="Rhoads" baseAuthorityYear="1895" box="[1963,2123,2919,2944]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="121" pageNumber="879" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="seminolus">L. seminolus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF826A3DF7A69D3E16DBB0B2" baseAuthorityName="Muller" baseAuthorityYear="1776" box="[2138,2267,2919,2944]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="121" pageNumber="879" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="borealis">L. borealis</taxonomicName>
, or 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF826A3DF6ED9D3E17ADB0B2" baseAuthorityName="Lesson &amp; Garnot" baseAuthorityYear="1826" box="[2321,2477,2919,2944]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="121" pageNumber="879" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="blossevilii">L. blossevilii</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF826A3DF6409D3E142FB0B2" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1831" box="[2492,2607,2919,2944]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="121" pageNumber="879" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Lasiurus</taxonomicName>
minors in the Red Bat group. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
